// Hand-curated barrel re-export for ts-rs generated types plus a few
// hand-mirrored shapes the engine surfaces but doesn't (yet) derive
// `TS` for. Anything in `./types/*.ts` is auto-regenerated by
// `cargo test -p nexus-types --features ts` — never hand-edit those.
//
// When the Rust side adds a new `#[derive(TS)]`, re-export here and
// (if it's a request/response wrapper) wire it into the relevant
// `./<domain>.ts` API module.

